ch mana use you guys do. I am constantly oom and always medding. Between casting darkness (unless necro around, or compulsive snare/rooter), keeping Vampiric Embrace up, and siphon strengh each mob.  <p><font +1><b>Seipher Voxnuro</b></font><br>Level 25 <b>ShadowKnight</b><img src="http://shoji420.tripod.com/shadow.gif" align="left>
